snippet.title: NARUTO X BORUTO Ultimate Ninja STORM CONNECTIONS — Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for action! NARUTO X BORUTO Ultimate Ninja STORM CONNECTIONS launches November 17, 2023! Choose from over 130 playable ninjas, including the menacing newcomers to the STORM series Delta, Boro, and Koji Kashin. Pre-order now! https://bnent.eu/Preorder-NSC

*Steam release date to be announced.
*Pre-orders for Nintendo Switch and Steam will start at a later date.

https://twitter.com/narutovideogame
